  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WITHSTAND THE ZOMBIE HORDE</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Defend your base against an increasingly difficult onslaught of zombies.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145830/extras/9bbe24279e8b0e64fb3b9a343fe70119.avif?t=1669571815\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ASSEMBLE YOUR ARSENAL</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Choose from a variety of weapons including pistols, shotguns, rifles and grenade launchers.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade your guns to increase your chances of survival against the horde.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145830/extras/93781dca622c1e0498afc408f4a6a8b6.avif?t=1669571815\" width=600 height=338 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FORTIFY YOUR BASE</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build fences and traps to provide some defense against the zombie horde.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145830/extras/98342fd9f7596893ea3087b41ec20673.avif?t=1669571815\" width=600 height=338 /></span>",
